            "id": 5941218,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉中美貿易角力又升高 10日線附近蹦極跳 收跌389點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達 H20 突遭禁令限制輸中，增加關稅不確定性，台股今日以 19,737.09 點、下跌 120.58 點開出，在電子、金融權值股疲軟下，指數一路下挫，最低跌逾 400 點，終場收 19468 點，下跌 389.67 點，跌約 2%，失守 5 日線及 10 日線，成交量 2852.34 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股跌多於漲，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 下跌 22 元，跌約 2%，收 855 元，並將於 17 日召開法說會；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 下跌 20 元，跌逾 1%，收 1365 元；，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 跌約 2%，日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 跌近 1%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 均收紅。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察本日類股走勢，上市櫃公司逾 1300 間下跌，AI 類股疲軟，矽光子部分，聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>) 跌約 6%，上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>) 跌約 4%；散熱部分，雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>) 跌停，奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 跌約 4%；機殼部分，晟銘電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3013:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3013\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3013-TW</a>) 跌近 7%，迎廣 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6117:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6117\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6117-TW</a>) 跌約 3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>豐藝、文曄分派股利亮眼，帶動電子通路股走強，豐藝 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6189-TW</a>) 漲約 9%，文曄 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3036:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3036\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3036-TW</a>) 漲約 5%，安馳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3528:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3528\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3528-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>百貨貿易類股成資金避風港，永邑 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2939:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2939\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2939-TW</a>) 漲逾 5%，台南 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5906:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5906\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5906-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，三商家購 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:2945:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2945\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2945-TW</a>) 漲約 3%，統一超 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2912:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2912\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2912-TW</a>) 漲近 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
